text.text:
in search of my first fish tank, hoping for guidance as an amateur. Unfortunately, I was met with a rather unhelpful and rude attitude from the staff. When I initially asked for recommendations, the employee I spoke with was reluctant to assist, leaving me feeling uncertain about my choices.

After deciding on a tank, I sought help in selecting a suitable filter and lighting. To my dismay, I encountered the same staff member, who bluntly told me to look for myself and seemed dismissive of my questions. This lack of support was incredibly frustrating, especially as a novice wanting to ensure a good environment for my future fish.

It’s disheartening to see that a business can afford to disregard customer service simply because they are doing well. Ultimately, I left the store empty-handed, choosing not to contribute to a place that doesn’t value its customers

text.text: The legendary aquarium shop in Singapore. The place is always packed with people all day yet the staff and owners are always friendly and helpful as ever assisting customers. And the price is reasonable. I got one pack of cherry shrimp 12 pieces for $7.20

text.text: Very interesting mini store for aquarium . I took quite numbers of product and fish. Get rejected by the store owner. Don’t wanna sell me more . Instead, he taught me how to build my fish tank. No rush. This is a journey of try and error. Impressive. Will go again.

text.text: Can find a lot of aquarium stuff here. Good place to get all the aquarium necessities at good price compared to the rest. Place is cramp, not recommended to bring kids along. If you are there to show your kids on all the fishes, better not.

text.text: Original old school local fish shop experience. You'll find all sorts and types of fishes and equipment at probably the best prices in SG. Service might not always be top notch but lady boss and her staff will always assist when help is needed, you just need to catch them at the right time as they're all so busy! This is my go-to LFS whenever I'm in the area.
